members.member:

Starts the per instance profiler for the given pin names (DPS or TDAU).

When callback is not registered to current tag.


This is code example:

string tag = "Tag1";
var pinNames = new List<string> { "pin01" };
int sampleRate = 4;
string callback = "someCallBack";
Prime.Base.ServiceStore<IPinService>.Service.StartPerInstanceProfile(tag, pinNames, callback, this.sessionContext);



The tag for the current profile.
The list of pins to profile.
The sampling interval of the measurements in ms.
The name of the callback to be trigerred for each tag.>
The session context of this operation.

